The paper discusses the challenges and potential solutions for making deep learning models interpretable and controllable by humans, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of visual analytics and information visualization techniques, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper focuses on image analysis and computer vision, which are covered under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
